summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5789 for the construction of A sewer to be known as the Fauntleroy Beach Intercepting Sewer, under Ordinance No. 76348, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
